<h3>Professional Staff Information</h3>
<ul>
	<li>
		Professional staff are located at the Cowichan branch, phone&nbsp;250-746-7661.</li>
	<li>
		Library Manager - Stephen R.&nbsp;Warren</li>
	<li>
		Adult Services Customer Services Librarian - Katey&nbsp;Stickle</li>
	<li>
		Children <span class="amp">&amp;</span> Youth Services Customer Services Librarian - Nariel&nbsp;Davis</li>
</ul></div>
  
