   <div class="tabbertab">
   <h3>Features</h3>
  <ul>
	<li>
		Two public access computers with internet access, word processing and&nbsp;printing</li>
	<li>
		Free wireless&nbsp;internet</li>
	<li>
		Research&nbsp;help</li>
</ul>  </div>
     
      <div class="tabbertab">
   <h3>Our Community</h3>
  <p>The Chemainus Library&nbsp;has occupied many locations&nbsp;over the years.&nbsp; From Mill Street, to the old post office building, to its current location, the branch has always been known as a friendly place with welcoming staff providing wonderful personal&nbsp;service.</p>  </div>
      
